ースファイル作成","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-811c-9595-f7a29c878502","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-810d-ad75-e0b117cd8a36","type":"paragraph","parent":"SQLiteで扱うデータベースファイルは、ファイルの拡張子が「.db」です。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8142-8374-fbe5496fb1ee","type":"paragraph","parent":"試しに、VSCode上で、「TEST.db」というファイルを作成してください。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f6-9c32-e062aa5af97a","type":"paragraph","parent":"TEST.dbを開いてください。上述した拡張機能をインストールしていれば、以下のように表示されます。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8152-8410-ddb1aed5a4cc","type":"image","parent":"![%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88_2024-11-11_13.51.57.png](https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/4faae8b3-4c31-46a7-898b-465eb6114fd9/49f141d1-8733-4188-a0a3-8f8d959fc549/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88_2024-11-11_13.51.57.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466RRVBGPVX%2F20250316%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20250316T053949Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEM3%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIHDDg30YA%2BEzpy0W3gY2uPNR6dqgloM3nwBOXkLMzF2SAiB%2B9p%2Fe7NtZ%2F9JMvKqrtIJStGhzwqkkQr1Hi8t7Mp6i8ir%2FAwglEAAaDDYzNzQyMzE4MzgwNSIMRpo4TiaJn4eXX7qwKtwDcARdDLrlqDC8wseH9rZOZL9%2Blnb9IW%2BKvqfGPNYj7WN%2F9AEwHDVfW3KKTVF1ms2On1O8uHNrKLCaeuaGHtAhCLzfKEZN3pCpDcqeHIV4zuJI8k2UKmsnEPexQOptTmOcdlbrxIHVUSvlTPTXxJU0wby%2BRroThYIbpU%2Boje02wYNUYP2sxqcEhLejPbYASFSE%2B7hZv9Q8OAioYwlbBTrIMtM217luOl27yqoixhdoWR0Jbf%2B45qjKpLEdqxOgMVY9AkcnA1n66WgVFkvuvmta8T30yH%2FjfHHzuw9FbLVDadbDoqknQXecMA%2BHJGHIFCAENjkLwjZCjq8iW%2FvFnA3jbYAUivcVO725BdsXa9mCI36qKWXoc12jiJdXtkRB0qa9z2j1bHqfpfqDBTTwO0bcx2M83XBYgewqRFwo1gO%2Br4nRRIpmDwcZcCFZhTfrkcyTFnHbwFtnYGG%2F7tR1e67UfjJQ7KGPDvEOXVXiY%2B64U0cDccSmqaVmXS9zupjQffx82ETQlhuQ1RdJfBCvBLP0tVZUYggpqHJvj5y7cEQETNnP%2Bt%2BP6P1o47HvpfcJVT